andidate model families\\n\\n- damped wave system  \\n- diffusion-like neural field  \\n- excitable medium  \\n- reaction–diffusion system  \\n- hybrid field \\\\+ readout system\\n\\n### Jack owns\\n\\n- engine implementation  \\n- performance engineering  \\n- parameter config plumbing  \\n- data structures for stepping the system  \\n- GPU / sparse solver integration if needed\\n\\n### Grant owns\\n\\n- selecting the model family  \\n- deriving or choosing equations  \\n- reasoning about stability  \\n- defining parameter ranges  \\n- specifying what behaviors are physically meaningful vs numerical artifacts\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\nagent_tickets/runs/20260322T022707Z/FW-M9-001_Freeze_a_versioned_simulator_result_bundle_contract_and_fair_baseline_design_note/stdout.jsonl:66:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_33\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc \\\"sed -n '1,220p' manifests/examples/milestone_1_demo.yaml\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"experiment_id: milestone_1_demo_motion_patch\\nmilestone: milestone_1\\nbrief_version: 1.0.0\\nhypothesis_version: 1.0.0\\nsubset_name: motion_minimal\\ncircuit_name: t4_t5_motion_patch\\nmodel_scope: T4/T5 carry morphology-resolved surface dynamics; upstream and downstream partners remain matched reduced or point models.\\nstimulus_family: moving_edge\\nstimulus_name: simple_moving_edge\\nprimary_metric: geometry_sensitive_null_direction_suppression_effect\\ncompanion_metrics:\\n  - response_latency_to_peak_ms\\n  - direction_selectivity_index\\n  - geometry_sensitive_shared_output_effect\\nsuccess_criteria_ids:\\n  - m1_nonzero_shared_output_effect\\n  - m1_latency_companion_effect\\n  - m1_geometry_dependence\\n  - m1_survives_stronger_baseline\\n  - m1_seed_parameter_stability\\nmust_show_outputs:\\n  - stimulus_overview\\n  - surface_vs_baseline_split_view\\n  - shared_output_trace_overlay\\n  - null_direction_suppression_comparison\\n  - latency_shift_comparis